title: Bug 47910 - ajc outjar jarfile does not contain MANIFEST.MF
description: When using the `outjar` option in ajc, the resulting jar file does not contain the expected `MANIFEST.MF` file.
OB: Currently, if outjar is used, the resulting jar file does not include the required `MANIFEST.MF` file.
EB: The `outjar` option should generate a valid jar file that includes the `MANIFEST.MF` file.
SR: Ensure that the `MANIFEST.MF` file is included in the jar file when using the `outjar` option in ajc.
